Relationships
LEAGUE → one League has many Teams
LEAGUE → one League has many Matchups (through week_number)
TEAM → one Team belongs to one League
TEAM → one Team has many Roster entries
TEAM → one Team has many Lineup entries
TEAM → one Team plays many Matchups (as home or away)
PLAYER → one Player can be on many Rosters (over time)
PLAYER → one Player has many Lineup entries
PLAYER → one Player has many Player Stats
ROSTER → resolves many-to-many between Team and Player
LINEUP → resolves who starts each week for each Team
MATCHUP → one Matchup belongs to one week
MATCHUP → one Matchup has one home Team and one away Team
MATCHUP → one Matchup has one winner Team
PLAYER_STATS → one Player has many weekly stats
PLAYER_STATS → one stat entry belongs to one Player and one week